Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼們 都碎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.58,0:00:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個光輝是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷囗在合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.04,0:00:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是 那傢伙的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.26,0:00:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.34,0:00:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是你做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.64,0:00:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.85,0:00:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法在寺院裡張開防禦牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.02,0:00:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這道結界只要不從我的意識內消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會消除陣內所有傷害我們的靈體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.11,0:00:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會認同的那樣的邪術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.32,0:00:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這四色之光是幽界深處保護我們疼愛我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偉大存在之靈力於現世展露之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.08,0:01:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那偉大的存在 就是你們法王廳的聖典內記載的四方的守護天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.21,0:01:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管表述的語言多麼不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.80,0:01:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽就是太陽 光芒就是光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.85,0:01:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使念誦的經文不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋求救贖的心卻相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.10,0:01:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把差異當成區分和虐待人的原因 是愚蠢的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.27,0:01:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的名義是屬於神的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.36,0:01:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人所統轄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.65,0:01:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為何我們的經文中沒有這些力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.45,0:01:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像你的咒文那樣召喚奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.62,0:01:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺院是為了使人和天使精靈會面的神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.62,0:01:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術師會自己在心中築造殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.00,0:01:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.93,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要相信眼睛看不到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.60,0:01:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有懷疑的餘地的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去看 去感覺 去觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.52,0:01:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個不得了的小姑娘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.08,0:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨龜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.84,0:03:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨 鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.51,0:03:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那種怪物會出現在現世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區巨鬼是無法進入這個結界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.86,0:04:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個結界對幽體有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對物體無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.81,0:04:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然出現了這種怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不創造機會的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造施展法術的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 司令員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等 那傢伙在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼樣也太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被踩扁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不會喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙很適應這種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我說的一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.62,0:05:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經覺得他超乎常人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到已經到如此地步了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣就幹掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用魔法只憑自己的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一個人類能達到這個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大傢伙獨有的頑強呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.73,0:06:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雜兵不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在手臂接好之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.78,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是川馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川馬就是讓旅行者在河中溺水的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.21,0:06:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只巨鬼連川馬也出現了為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雨 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個怪物卻會用魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川馬是中位靈格的水妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同族的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很容易驅使沒有自我的低級元素們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨天的川馬是非常危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有視覺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是順著自己的欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉罕見的活人的幽體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.07,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅有獸鬼 連巨鬼和川馬也出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意料之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.37,0:07:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.95,0:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.96,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太逞強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿獸鬼做對手還可以 但
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是和敵人周旋 爭取些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女小姐就趁機念咒又吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.71,0:07:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.13,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.01,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好保護喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.43,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.14,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.53,0:07:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼短時間內能把風元素活用到如此程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.58,0:07:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法解放你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在你旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我沒想過這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.46,0:08:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我的半身一樣的另一個被鎖著的靈魂在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我被黑暗包圍著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這也要結柬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.93,0:08:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼至少我要在暴風兩中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.39,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓半身被撕成碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.27,0:08:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風之精靈啊 給予我力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無差別摔跤比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個馬蟾蜍很適合做我的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你隨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也容易理解這邊的傢伙 對我的路子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 趴下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單槍匹馬就把那個怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快當廢物使了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候我什麼也辦不成啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是何等的景象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.26,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神靈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德·卡普拉... ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.84,0:09:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須趕緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.39,0:09:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比這層幽界更深一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個寺院建成之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位於這個山丘的神殿的幽體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.69,0:09:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之元素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.70,0:09:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.13,0:10:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻擊都被水牆阻擋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.26,0:10:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與此相比 我卻不能防住所有的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到水花會有這樣的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被壓制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.02,0:10:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為魔法初學者 已是無計可施了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.36,0:10:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克的樣子不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.66,0:10:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.13,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.39,0:10:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止會發射水花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點就在地上淹死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多虧這些我也明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風的力量不止是把東西斬斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 精靈們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能斬開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捲起來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.85,0:11:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 賽路畢克那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.03,0:11:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 會掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水從川馬身上離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.17,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是魔法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼 看見了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是水的精靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.56,0:12:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒現在和水的精靈成為一體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.07,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被附體啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水的眷屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流經此地的谷河的精靈們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵從古老的誓約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清洗汙染這片土地的惡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以水底的貴婦人之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向元素靈們發令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這土地上的邪惡靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用激流沖回冥界的黑暗之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.89,0:13:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.31,0:13:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是水本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集吧 我的眷屬們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集吧 聚集吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.32,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻滾 流動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.99,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這回又怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得不太妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河水泛濫 朝這邊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快進來 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被捲進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多洛皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.26,0:14:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼 怪物們都被沖走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 我們得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.10,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人 魔女大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辦到了 特羅皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.86,0:14:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特羅皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒 已經好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子全部幹掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.16,0:14:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多再不醒過來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.17,0:14:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 和水精同步太強失去自我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法術解不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎廑會 希凱兒小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.22,0:15:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在施術的時候被強行喚回會發生什麼事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在史爾基已經去了幽界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.02,0:15:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剛才的水精融為一體 現在一定被困在這流水中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.94,0:15:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在心回來之前就喚醒 不知道會對身體産生什麼影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍有不慎 也許會不能回復自我變成廢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底要怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那個 我記得這個時候要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個杖打拍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.08,0:15:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以一定的節奏打拍子 令施術者的精神集中在現世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.59,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科羅拉這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,節奏是七·七·七拍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打三次七拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.35,0:15:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激烈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捲起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用人語表達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.64,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人焦慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.15,0:15:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和精靈們心靈交融非常重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可被其吞噬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.53,0:16:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此魔法師會在施術是用杖打拍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.28,0:16:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來確保自己的意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.41,0:16:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂魔道 絶不是與力量融為一體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂魔道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.96,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼 打起精神來 魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.91,0:16:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.96,0:16:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.73,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.57,0:17:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒找到那兩人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能亂動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.62,0:17:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急 現在希凱兒在尋找兩人的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的賣任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我沉溺於力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.51,0:17:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是再做好一些的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.09,0:17:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.64,0:17:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.51,0:17:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這麼緊張的話 平時做得到的事也會失敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.94,0:17:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話嚇到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拯救了這個村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人會責備你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.91,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 感覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.87,0:18:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.38,0:18:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.96,0:18:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 到底要怎樣才能做到那麼厲害的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助天使和精靈的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救這個村子的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.94,0:18:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家教典裡的守護東西南北的四大天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有在建起寺院之前 這片土地祭祀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河流的精靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可底的貴婦人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.50,0:19:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我曾經聽爺爺說過這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.09,0:19:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片山丘以前建有祭祀河神的神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.01,0:19:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為長期被遺忘 這次又突然叫出來的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河流的精靈有些生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此村子才會被水淹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.43,0:19:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不成熟的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房子再建就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.61,0:19:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能這樣活著 都是靠你的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.07,0:19:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.66,0:19:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我心中對村民的憤怒導致的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.79,0:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人 可以的話在這個廣場的西邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能建個祭祀河神的小祠堂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就建吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寬容也是神的教誨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣的小孩子也能引起那樣的奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰都可以用魔法的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.14,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用魔法要花很長時間修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.64,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是把願望傳達給天使和精靈你們也能辦的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.77,0:20:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個方法祭司很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.04,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子你才是沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.00,0:20:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處亂走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.29,0:20:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖那個小個子的福已經好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先跟你道個謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.17,0:20:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不起你這個拯救村子的英雄的謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.51,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甭抬舉我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.85,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個四處大吵大鬧的小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.18,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我有想要給你的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我父親從海員那裡賭贏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種小尺寸小孩子也揮的起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.53,0:20:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能收下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.16,0:21:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個老人的餞別禮罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.21,0:21:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是逃出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從家計和病重的母親那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.13,0:21:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從所有沉重繁瑣的東西中逃出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想也真是奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.84,0:21:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得是勇敢的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也覺得是天真的逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想是那個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才說你們上年紀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了老頭 我那個叫野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和天真的夢想等級可不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要證明自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.82,0:21:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本事是貨真價實的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 東西我就心懷感激的收下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.75,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.54,0:21:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就行動是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.96,0:21:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個寺院的魔法效果還沒完全消散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住上一晚傷囗就該好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.51,0:21:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒有等待的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.30,0:22:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早一刻也好 趕緊出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.93,0:22:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.81,0:22:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去去就回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.74,0:22:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.61,0:22:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要發呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.07,0:22:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.26,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.54,Preview,,0,0,0,,腐朽之物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.05,0:24:10.13,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}是幽界的黑暗領域 克里科特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.26,0:24:14.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你來殿後 保護女人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你的靈魂和這樣的\N克里科特很相配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.64,0:24:22.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你在窺視深淵的時候 \N深淵也在窺視你
